k. 
 Alternate Drug Test Coordinator (ADTC).

a. ADTCs must be at pay grade E-6 or higher or a member of the Command Cadre;

b. Units are authorized two ADTCs. Requests for more than two ADTCs must be sent to 
PSC-PSD-FS for review and approval;

c. Each ADTC must be designated in writing annually. At least one ADTC must have 
access to the testing register in WebDTP and specimen collection materials;

d. ADTCs are responsible for implementing the processes and procedures set forth in 
this Instruction, the contracted laboratory’s procedures, and on CG-PSC-PSD-FS’s 
CG portal site at https://cg.portal.uscg.mil/units/psc/FS/default.aspx;

e. ADTCs are responsible for making testing register entries in WebDTP, if the ADTC 
